ğŸŒ APIs
Template APIs

GET /api/templates â†’ list templates (latest versions, active flag)

Survey APIs

POST /api/surveys â†’ create survey from template + assignees + deadline

GET /api/surveys â†’ list surveys (filter: owner/admin)

GET /api/surveys/{id} â†’ get survey detail (metadata + assignments with status)

Response APIs

POST /api/surveys/{id}/responses â†’ save/submit answers for assignee

GET /api/surveys/{id}/responses â†’ raw responses (per user, for admin only)

Summary APIs

GET /api/surveys/{id}/summary â†’ aggregated analytics per question

